    <!-- Welcome / First Launch -->
    <string name="welcome_title">Boyei malamu</string>
    <string name="welcome_sovereignty">Fungola na yo.\nMbongo na yo.\nBonsomi na yo.</string>
    <string name="welcome_desc">Mbongo na yo ebombami te na aplikasio oyo. Ezali na blockchain, na se ya bokonzi ya fungola na yo ya secrɛ.\n\nAplikasio oyo ebombi kaka fungola na yo na kobatela. Tokoki te kosimba mbongo na yo.\n\nYeba: Tokens mosusu (USDC, USDT) ekoki kokangama na bakabisi na bango. Mpo na bonsomi mobimba, salelá ETH ya mbotama to tokens oyo ekangami na moto moko te.</string>
    <string name="welcome_warning_title">Fungola na yo = Mbongo na yo</string>
    <string name="welcome_warning_desc">Soki obungisi fungola na yo ya secrɛ to opesi yango na moto mosusu, obungisi bokonzi ya mbongo na yo mpo na libela.\n\nNzela ya kozongisa ezali te. Ekipi ya lisungi ekoki kosalisa yo te. Oyo ezali ndenge ya bozwi ya solo.\n\nBómba ntango nyonso bakopi ya fungola na yo na kobatela.</string>
    <string name="welcome_opensource">Logiciel ya source ouverte. Talá, kondima kaka te.</string>
    <string name="welcome_start">Nayebi, tóbanda</string>

